  * resynch with debian.
  * really use automake1.9.
  * remove savedefault feature from update-grub because it is broken by
    gfxboot patches.
  * reduces x86_64 variants to "amd64".
  * bump compat level to 5.
  * drop reiser4 patches.
  * switch to dpatch.
  * drop debian xpm based splash screens.
  * update to grub-splashscreen v7.

