  * Make postinstall script
  * Create manpage for grubinst
  * Make grubinst more flexible
  * Address bugs 15227 and 15163 (packaging and clue endowment)

 -- Steve Dunham <dunham@debian.org>  Thu,  1 Jan 1998 00:38:22 -0500

